---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To get a (pseudo-) random integer between, say, 60 and 75, we can do this:
import java.util.Random;
Random r = new Random();
r.nextInt(16); //0 to 15 inclusive
r.nextInt(16) + 60; //shifted up by 60, 0-15 becomes 60-75
